              through a MCP server for all internal use cases.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="mx-auto h-12 w-0 bg-neutral-300 lg:w-px dark:bg-neutral-700"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid items-start gap-x-8 gap-y-4 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div
            class="flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-dashed border-neutral-300 p-8 pt-7 dark:border-neutral-700"
          >
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-4 text-neutral-500">Context</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-1">
              <span
